      "actionDate": "2025-09-15",
      "actionDesc": "Reported to House",
      "text": "<p><strong>University of Utah Research Park Act</strong></p><p>This bill confirms the use by the University of Utah of approximately 593 acres of specified nonfederal land in Salt Lake City, Utah, as a university research park and for related university purposes (including development of student housing and a transit hub) as a valid public purpose.</p>",
